OL,3,GNorthern Ireland
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA few showers around in the
OL,6,Fmorning but still plenty of dry and
OL,7,Fbright spells. Drier in the afternoon,
OL,8,Falthough the odd shower still
OL,9,Fpossible, with longer sunny spells
OL,10,Fdeveloping. Mostly light winds but
OL,11,Fbreezy near coasts.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FIt will be a dry evening with
OL,14,Fsome late sunny spells before turning
OL,15,Fcloudier from the west. Becoming
OL,16,Fcloudy for all overnight with
OL,17,Foutbreaks of rain spreading eastwards.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
