OL,3,GNorthern Ireland
OL,4,
OL,5,CSaturday:FA cloudy day with rain
OL,6,Fpushing eastwards and turning heavy at
OL,7,Ftimes. Rain clearing to clear spells
OL,8,Fand scattered showers later in the day.
OL,9,
OL,10,COutlook for Sunday to Tuesday:FMostly
OL,11,Fcloudy with heavy showers Sunday.
OL,12,FDrier for a time Monday with sunny
OL,13,Fspells, then rain spreading east
OL,14,Flater. Strong winds at times Tuesday
OL,15,Fwith rain clearing to heavy showers.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
